From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Victor Momplet <mompletvictor@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 16 Jul 2026 18:35:39 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] feat: bundle Inter as the house sans

Inter (OFL, license at android/INTER-OFL.txt) replaces the platform
grotesque across all styles; it carries the 'tnum' feature the numeric
styles require.
---
 android/INTER-OFL.txt                         |  92 ++++++++++++++++++
